# UI Toolkit Rules (NOT UGUI)

## Project Policy (This Project)

- Per `[.cursor/rules/project-overview.mdc]`, **UI Toolkit is the only UI stack used for new UI** in this project.
- **Unity UI Canvas / UGUI must not be used for new UI work** here; `unity-ui-canvas.mdc` is reference-only unless the overview is updated.

## Project Structure

UI lives under `Assets/Scripts` per code-organization. Controllers, Views, ViewModels, UXML, and USS sit under `Runtime/UI/`; Editor UI scripts under `Editor/`.

```
Assets/
└── Scripts/
    ├── Runtime/
    │   └── UI/                 # UI controllers (code-organization: Runtime/UI)
    │       ├── Controllers/
    │       │   └── MainMenuController.cs
    │       ├── Views/
    │       │   └── MainMenuView.cs
    │       ├── ViewModels/
    │       │   └── HealthViewModel.cs
    │       ├── UXML/
    │       │   └── MainMenu.uxml
    │       └── USS/
    │           └── MainMenu.uss
    └── Editor/
        └── UIBuilderExtensions.cs
```

